value.0: Formally the SpecForce 5th Regiment, the Infiltrators were the elite commandos of Rebel Alliance Special Forces. Chosen for both skill and motivation, Infiltrators are tasked with the riskiest missions. Capable of entering the most heavily guarded Imperial installations, starships and planets, Infiltrators act as saboteurs, abducters, rescue operators, spies and assassins.

There are a variety of different kinds of armor intended to defend against the harsh enviroments of space, deflect the impact of blaster bolts and protect versus all types of damage that can be found on a battlefield. These suits are usually built in with a personal shield generator.
